<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Potash Corp cut on price.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Potash Corp cut on price.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- J.P. Morgan Securities said it downgraded Potash Corp of Saskatchewan Inc to market perform from buy on the basis of its price.</p>
<p>-- Cited 44 percent rise from 52-week low and 11 percent rise since announcing terms for  Kali und Salz AG purchase.</p>
<p>-- Also cited risk associated with European regulatory issues related to purchase.</p>
<p>-- NYSE-listed shares fell 1-1/4 to 85-3/8.</p>
<p>((-- Wall Street desk, 212-859-1730))</p>
